4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become an AI Machine Learning Engineer" which is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge. The course aims to prepare students for a career as a data scientist and provides the necessary skills to build machine learning models. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes per week. The class size is limited to 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. The instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena, who are experienced professionals in the field of AI and machine learning. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and teaches students how to create predictive models using libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. Students also gain experience with algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course emphasizes real-life case studies and provides hands-on experience in developing AI projects. The syllabus and content can be delivered in English or Spanish, with live classes conducted in the language of the student's campus. For more information, visit the [4Geeks Academy website](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop